* Mon Mar 5 2018 Chris Tessmer <chris.tessmer@onyxpoint.com> - 6.4.0-0
- Changed the internal implementation of `ssh::client::host_config_entry`:
  - Switched over to `ssh_config` resources from augeasproviders_ssh
  - Removed concat + erb templates
- Users can customize additional SSH client options using `ssh_config`
  - This brings ssh_config management in line with sshd_config
- Added `ssh.aug` lens to pluginsync directory

